node.text:
On this day 22 years ago @RestaurantGordonRamsay opened its doors for the first time, and today we're delighted to announce that @Chef.Mattabe has been named Co-Chef Patron. Thank you to Matt for his outstanding leadership through the years, and to all of our guests who have been a part of this incredible journey. 

#RestaurantGordonRamsay
